headline: Generac Unveils the Most Powerful Air-Cooled Home Standby Generator on the Market
summary: Generac Holdings, Inc. (NYSE: GNRC), a leading global designer, manufacturer and provider of energy technology solutions and other power products, today announced its latest home standby generator design, including the new 28kW model, the most powerful air-cooled home standby available in the market.
